de.geofencing.system.device

Class Device

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.geofencing.system.device.Device
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Device
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a device which is registered on the GeofencingSystem. The deviceID is the primary identifier, the mail address is for verification. The time stamp lastTimeUpdated shows the last time, the device updated its beacons. The optional Firebase token is used to send notifications to the Device.
    Author:
    Markus Thral
